abstract: Katie Ledecky sets new world record for women’s 800-meter freestyle at Arena Pro Swim Series event in Austin, Tex.
lead_paragraph: Ledecky broke her own world record in the women’s 800-meter freestyle in the Arena Pro Swim Series event in Austin, Tex.

headline.main: Katie Ledecky Breaks Her Own Record
